race.description: All Roof Australia Country Boosted Handicap (Bm58)
race.comment: LADY ALABAMA (2) made it two wins on the bounce last time out when a sharp winner in fast time over 1310m at this track. Confidence is high and can make it three straight victories. MONARCH EXPRESS (1) has a good record at this track and trip and looks to have strengthened over the break. Produced a solid set of figures first-up when he surged late for a game second over 1106m at Grafton. Can race closer from the draw and prove hard to stop. GOLD PUMA (4) drifted back from the low draw and savaged the line late when fourth over 1400m at the Gold Coast. Won here two-back and not to be underestimated. GAMING (6) scored a determined win last time out over 1400m at Grafton. In the mix.
